The  semiclassical approximation is applicable only for .  Eq. () implies  that for the tunneling through the barrier with  (which is the case for the tunneling from dS space to Minkowski space in our model) the action  is always negative, . This means that the decay time of dS space to Minkowski space is exponentially smaller than the 
